title: Zeina
description: Every moment is a doorway to another moment. This collection is for the vintage loving souls who are also dancing on the edge of modernity. Honoring every woman who chooses to be a merge of different times, who allows herself to carry a time machine that only she has access to, a time machine where she can glimpse back and forth on different sides of herself.
